  18 Jan 2009; Robert A <r_a@lavabit.com>
  bison-2.3.ebuild, bison-2.4-r1.ebuild, bison-2.4.1.ebuild:
  new use flag "liby" which installs the static library liby

  25 Dec 2008; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org> bison-2.4.1.ebuild:
  KEYWORDS="" until there is further testing.

*bison-2.4.1 (22 Dec 2008)

